
STUDENT
- $podman login

- $mkdir -p .config/flatpak

- flatpak remote-ls

- flatpak install org.mozilla.firefox

- flatpak list

- flatpak run org.mozilla.firefox 2> /dev/null
start and send errors to dev/null
- flatpak uninstall com.redhat.Platform org.mozilla.firefox


INTERN
$mkdir -p .config/flatpak
flatpak remote-add --no-gpg-verify --if-not-exists flathup --user  https://dl.flathub.org/repo/flathub.flatpakrepo 

flatpak list --user

flatpak search --user Chromium
flatpak install --user org.chromium.Chromium
flatpak list
flatpak run org.chromium.Chromium 2> /dev/null


flatpak uninstall --user org.chromium.Chromium

